results.name: adidas Gazelle Disney The Little Mermaid
results.story: Drawn from ‘The Little Mermaid Collection,’ the Disney x adidas Gazelle ‘Max’ gives the nod to Prince Eric’s Old English Sheepdog. Standing in for Max’s fluffy coat is shaggy suede detailing on the heel tab and signature three-stripes, while the character’s nose is displayed front and center on the leather tongue tag. The rest of the upper is constructed from off-white leather, produced using sustainable dye technologies that cut down on the use of water, energy and chemicals.

results.name: adidas Ozweego Disney The Little Mermaid
results.story: Launching as part of ‘The Little Mermaid Collection,’ the Disney x adidas Ozweego ‘Ursula’ takes inspiration from the villainous sea witch who conspires to rule the sea kingdom. Neutral off-white and beige tones are applied to a textile upper with tentacle-embossed leather overlays. A leather tongue tag displays dual adidas and Disney branding on the exterior side. The interior side features Ursula’s illustrated likeness, along with a quote that reads ‘Life is full of tough choices, isn’t it?’

adidas NMD R1 Disney The Little Mermaid
results.story: Drawn from the ‘The Little Mermaid Collection,’ the Disney x adidas NMD_R1 ‘Flotsam and Jetsam’ draws inspiration from Ursula’s moray eel henchmen. A monochromatic off-white finish floods the knit upper, produced with sustainable dye technologies that require less water, energy and chemicals. A scaly texture distinguishes the leather heel patch, while the leather tongue tag features adidas and Disney branding. The interior tongue is decorated with a graphic depicting the villainous duo, along with a quote that assures the wearer, ‘Don’t be scared.’

Kyrie 7 EP 'Pale Ivory'
results.story: The Nike Kyrie 7 EP ‘Pale Ivory’ carries an off-white mesh upper that reveals swirling pastel colors on the textile inlay. A raised Swoosh in pink and black adorns the lateral side, while a printed blue Swoosh decorates the opposite side. A split design is similarly used on the rubber outsole and heel overlay, featuring equations and charts on one side, and colorful doodles on the other. On the performance front, the sneaker rides on a lightweight Phylon midsole with an Air Zoom Turbo unit in the forefoot. This EP edition features a rugged rubber outsole designed for outdoor courts.

Jordan 13 Retro Gym Red Flint Grey (GS)
results.story: Built for big kids, the Air Jordan 13 Retro GS ‘Red Flint’ brings back the same color blocking used on the OG ‘Flint’ colorway released in 1998. Like its predecessor, this pair features a white leather base and grey synthetic suede overlays that extend to the Phylon midsole. The older shoe’s blue accents are replaced by Gym Red on the interior tongue, collar lining and mesh overlays, featuring reflective detailing for added visibility in low-light conditions. Underfoot, the panther paw outsole utilizes herringbone traction pods for optimal grip.

Jordan 13 Retro Gym Red Flint Grey
results.story: The Air Jordan 13 Retro ‘Red Flint’ takes its design cues from the OG ‘Flint’ colorway from 1998. Gym Red replaces the older shoe’s blue accents, appearing on the interior tongue, collar lining and the reflective mesh overlays that dominate the upper. The rest of the build incorporates white leather and grey synthetic suede, which extends to the midsole and collar. The latter is embellished with the 13’s signature holographic eye, joining the sneaker’s panther paw outsole in channeling MJ’s Black Cat persona.

Dejounte Murray x Two WXY 'My Home'
results.story: Inspired by the NBA star, the Dejounte Murray x New Balance Two WXY ‘My Home’ features bold contrasting hues on a breathable textile upper fortified with Kinetic Stitch detailing throughout the quarter panel. The mid-top rides on a full-length FuellCell foam midsole, reinforced by a rigid midsole shank for torsional stability. Underfoot, oversized NB branding adorns a data-driven outsole that blends translucent rubber with grippy gum rubber that wraps up the sidewalls.

results.name: Nike LeBron 18 Minneapolis Lakers
results.story: The Nike LeBron 18 ‘Lakers Heritage’ takes inspiration from the NBA franchise’s origins in Minneapolis, Minnesota, the state colloquially known as the ‘Land of 10,000 Lakes.’ The sneaker’s color scheme reflects the early road uniforms of the Minneapolis Lakers, highlighted by a powder blue tongue and a flexible collar in University Gold. Matching yellow accents are interspersed throughout the black KnitPosite 2.0 upper. The sneaker rides on a Cushlon midsole that works in tandem with a full-length Zoom Air unit, which is partially housed within a visible Max Air unit under the heel.

results.name: ZX 1K Boost 'Bold Logo Graphic - Solar Red'
Jordan 13 Retro Gym Red Flint Grey (TD)
results.story: The Air Jordan 13 Retro TD ‘Red Flint’ delivers a scaled-down version of the iconic silhouette, rendered in color blocking that recalls the OG ‘Flint’ release from 1998. This pair discards the blue accents of the original, replacing them with a bold Gym Red finish on the interior tongue, collar lining and reflective mesh overlays. The rest of the upper pairs white leather with grey synthetic suede paneling that extends from the midfoot and around the heel. An embroidered Jumpman atop the tongue is joined by a second Jumpman icon within the sneaker’s holographic eye.
